data.description: Lovely 2 family!! First floor unit freshly painted. Each floor features a galley kitchen, 2 bedrooms, living room, and dining room with hardwood floors throughout, and a full bath. The roof, siding, and windows were installed 10 years ago. Each floor has a gas stove, separate heating, and separate electric circuit breakers. Conveniently located near school, train, shopping, and major routes.
